translator.minionModel
Class MinionIdentifier

java.lang.Object
  translator.minionModel.MinionIdentifier
Direct Known Subclasses:
MinionBoolVariable, MinionBoundsVariable, MinionConst, MinionConstant, MinionDiscreteSVariable, MinionDiscreteVariable, MinionSBoundsVariable
public abstract class MinionIdentifier
extends Object

Each variable has a relative index (index concerning the domain type of the variables only) and an absolute index (index concerning all variables) and can only be identified by that. Notes (ian): 1. Variable ids are all given relative to the start of a variable type to allow insertion of new variables.

Author:
andrea, ian
